{"tid":2072663,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"想問下如果狗狗有呢啲問題 大家會點做","createTime":"2020-06-20T17:36:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-26T06:35:21.000Z","uid":157014,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"8abb162ea0f7844cab6c7fe7fd392c9e4052e3f0","tid":2072663,"uid":157014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T17:36:37.000Z","msg":"屋企最近領養左隻唐狗女 衣家8個月大左右 但係佢出街會搶住條繩走 所以特登買左呢款choke 繩教佢 平時用會配埋條胸帶一齊用 佢一衝就用條choke 繩比signal 佢 要佢sit定左先繼續行 但佢出到街 靜靜地既地方都有啲用 但去啲地方佢就會分心 周圍望 點叫點choke 佢都唔理你 咁既話大家會點做 有時都會怕choke 得太勁會整傷佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而且佢有時見到陌生人 車 同狗都會想撲或者衝過去 應該點樣教識佢唔好咁猴擒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/P4yf0yL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP4yf0yL.jpg&h=fe363ff6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/67i0seR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F67i0seR.jpg&h=fdb843e3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cfc35f541d90c33c90eac713cb0b034bef95323d","tid":2072663,"uid":123456,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T17:38:10.000Z","msg":"想奶巴打隻腳<br />\n比你一路屌一路chok<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9083e59300df9e680f0008bb8459209345643942","tid":2072663,"uid":104138,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T17:38:19.000Z","msg":"上 youtube search Eric Ko超級馴犬師 會有教學"},{"pid":"e6416eec26ba240a036d0deaa683b9c690d3dd57","tid":2072663,"uid":127929,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T17:38:34.000Z","msg":"@衲dee <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c18e0b048f26cc9540fd794a06b34945eacf4cdc","tid":2072663,"uid":215026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T21:46:29.000Z","msg":"留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />搶到手軟"},{"pid":"8c8929e2e3629a